sitter (0.3.1.0~bionic) bionic; urgency=high

  * Use fluid-settings.
  * Separated the .ini files, one per plugin.
  * Fixed options.
  * Ignore the seed.txt file.
  * Various updates to compile with other contribs.
  * Fixed a title.
  * Removed Cassandra as a dependency.
  * The processing now happens in a thread. If the thread dies, auto-restart.
  * Enhanced error generator and use JSON instead of XML.
  * Added a backup-etc package to the project.

